## `README.md`

```markdown
# Mustang Station 3 - Paint & Body Prep

> **Model:** Mustang  
> **Group:** Paint & Body  
> **Station:** 3  
> **Purpose:** Strip, clean, prep, and disassemble for paint

---

## Navigation

- [Preparation](docs/preparation.md)
- [Body Prep](docs/body-prep.md)
- [Hood](docs/hood.md)
- [Fender Extension](docs/fender-extension.md)
- [Handwritten Notes](docs/handwritten-notes/)

---

**Safety First:** Respirator required for 360-4 metal cleaner. Safety glasses for all sanding/grinding.
```

